_sText:
Hey Everyone,

This was a CS:S map made for the mapping competition over at TWHL. It's not intended to be run as a full server map, nor is it in an assigned game-mode. Basically you can play it as a fun little deathmatch type map.

Have fun exploring. :)


Credit:
Komaokc for the skybox "sky08" -> see his profile on gamebanana, his skyboxes are incredible.

TopHATTwaffle for the waterfall texture -> he has a bunch of interesting running water
textures: http://gamebanana.com/css/textures/2665

Thanks to: Grim, Blitz, Ant, PB, Strider, RabidMonkey and anyone else who commented or gave critiques about the map.
Cheers all,
